OL,3,CIs this Britain's most dangerous road
OL,4,Cjunction?
OL,6,FA road junction in Staffordshire has
OL,7,Fbeen dubbed by locals as 'Britain's
OL,8,Fmost dangerous' after 13 crashes in
OL,9,Fjust six weeks.
OL,11,FMisleading give-way signs and faded
OL,12,Froad markings have been blamed for the
OL,13,Fhigh number of crashes at the junction
OL,14,Fbetween Draycott Cross Road, Delphouse
OL,15,FRoad, Brookhouse Road and The Green in
OL,16,FCheadle near Stoke-on-Trent.
OL,18,FLocal pub landlord Conor Devine has
OL,19,Fkept a tally of the number of crashes
OL,20,Fon a blackboard outside his pub.
