OL,3,CIs this Britain's most dangerous road
OL,4,Cjunction?
OL,6,FHe said: "I've heard every crash. The
OL,7,Flast one sounded like a bomb going off.
OL,9,F"Nobody is stopping in both
OL,10,Fdirections. There have been three very
OL,11,Fserious crashes.
OL,13,F"I don't want to be coming out of the
OL,14,Fpub one day to find someone dead in
OL,15,Fthe middle of the road."
