OL,3,CIs this Britain's most dangerous road
OL,4,Cjunction?
OL,6,FAbbey Bentley, whose home CCTV has
OL,7,Fcaptured the crashes at the junction,
OL,8,Fsaid: "I was just sat at my desk,
OL,9,Fworking away and I heard these
OL,10,Fcrunches, and I thought 'oh no not
OL,11,Fagain' because you just know the noise
OL,12,Fwhen you hear it.
OL,14,F"We've had an accident on all four
OL,15,Fsides of the junction now, it just
OL,16,Fmakes you wonder if the next one will
OL,17,Fbe through the front door."
