OL,3,CIs this Britain's most dangerous road
OL,4,Cjunction?
OL,6,FStaffordshire County Council said it
OL,7,Fhas painted new 'give-way' road
OL,8,Fmarkings, has cut back some vegetation
OL,9,Fand has put in temporary advance
OL,10,Fwarning signs.
OL,12,FIt added it wants to go further, and
OL,13,Fis considering changing it from a
OL,14,F'give-way' to a 'stop' junction.
